    "In Fig. 8a, the ResNet middle layer feature output image is displayed, with each grid in different layouts representing a feature map.",
    "In Fig. 8b, the feature layer output images of Swin Transformer Large and Swin Transformer Base are showcased.",
    "Due to the depth and complexity of the models, each convolutional layer extracts features at different levels and abstraction.",
    "As a result, the feature maps output from multiple intermediate layers can synthetically represent various visual information within the input image.",
    "This aids in better understanding the decision-making process and performance of the deep learning model."
